Comment: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:43.54,SUB,,0,0,0,karaoke,我啊 对一行同学……
Comment: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.32,SUB,,0,0,0,karaoke,在交往之后没多久就发生了事故
Comment: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.52,SUB,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也想救她
Comment: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:52.86,SUB,,0,0,0,karaoke,要保护好她哦
Comment: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:53.54,SUB,,0,0,0,karaoke,好！
Comment: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:58.60,SUB,,0,0,0,karaoke,快点直实
Comment: 0,0:00:58.80,0:00:59.41,SUB,,0,0,0,karaoke,一行同学
